# ===================================
# INSTRUCTIONS
# ===================================

# 1. RAZORPAY SETUP
#    a) Create account at https://razorpay.com
#    b) Go to Dashboard → Settings → API Keys
#    c) Copy Key ID and Key Secret
#    d) For development, use TEST keys
#    e) For production, use LIVE keys

# 2. BANK ACCOUNT SETUP
#    a) Go to Admin Dashboard → Bank Account
#    b) Add your bank details:
#       - Account Holder Name
#       - Bank Name
#       - Account Number (8-17 digits)
#       - IFSC Code (format: AAAA0AAAAAA)
#       - Account Type (Savings/Current)
#    c) Razorpay will send 2 microdeposits (₹1-5)
#    d) Verify by entering deposit amounts
#    e) Account verified - payments auto-settle!

# 3. TEST KEYS vs LIVE KEYS
#    TEST: Won't actually charge money, good for testing
#    LIVE: Will charge real money, use after testing complete

# 4. SECURITY NOTES
#    - NEVER commit this file to git
#    - NEVER share Key Secret with anyone
#    - Key ID is public (ok to put in frontend)
#    - Key Secret stays in backend only

# 5. SWITCHING FROM TEST TO LIVE
#    Step 1: Thoroughly test with test keys
#    Step 2: Go to Razorpay → Settings → API Keys
#    Step 3: Click "Live" tab
#    Step 4: Copy live keys
#    Step 5: Update this file with live keys
#    Step 6: Restart backend server
#    Step 7: Verify first real payment
#    Step 8: Monitor settlement to bank

# 6. WEBHOOK SETUP (Optional but recommended)
#    a) In Razorpay Dashboard → Settings → Webhooks
#    b) Add Webhook URL: https://yourdomain.com/payment/webhook
#    c) Events to enable:
#       - payment.authorized
#       - payment.captured
#       - payment.failed
#    d) Copy Webhook Secret
#    e) Add to this file as RAZORPAY_WEBHOOK_SECRET

# ===================================
# PAYMENT METHODS AVAILABLE
# ===================================
# UPI: Google Pay, PhonePe, BHIM, etc.
# Cards: Visa, Mastercard, Amex
# Net Banking: HDFC, ICICI, Axis, SBI, etc.
# Wallets: PayZapp, Freecharge, etc.

# ===================================
# CHARGES & FEES
# ===================================
# UPI/Net Banking: ~1-2% + ₹0-3 fixed
# Debit Card: ~0.7-1% + ₹0-5 fixed
# Credit Card: ~2% + ₹0-5 fixed
# International: Higher fees

# Example:
# Customer pays: ₹500
# Razorpay takes: ₹14 (2.8%)
# You receive: ₹486

# ===================================
# SETTLEMENT INFO
# ===================================
# Settlement Type: T+1 (Next business day)
# Settlement Frequency: Daily
# Settlement Account: Your configured bank account
# Settlement Process: Automatic (Razorpay handles)

# Example Settlement:
# Day 1 (Mon 5PM): Customer pays ₹590
#   - Razorpay receives payment
#   - Fee deducted: ~₹14
#   - Net: ₹576
#
# Day 2 (Tue 10AM): Settlement
#   - ₹576 deposited to your bank account
#   - No action needed!

